  "detailed_description": "<strong>DEITY DRIVING</strong> mushes adventure and arcade elements – drive around as a submissive car, bump into strangers and enjoy your involuntary vacation!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213460/extras/8fe6cad625a201f1018aac2fe8e765fe.poster.avif?t=1579727135\" width=596 height=266 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213460/extras/8fe6cad625a201f1018aac2fe8e765fe.webm?t=1579727135\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213460/extras/8fe6cad625a201f1018aac2fe8e765fe.mp4?t=1579727135\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>There are three different paths and endings, seeing them all takes about 20 to 30 minutes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1213460/extras/518a4065a283afcb6036e9ac1d880f5c.avif?t=1579727135\" width=250 height=163 /></span><br><br><i>Features:</i><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Fully voiced<br></li><li>A relaxed ride with dogs and demons</li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>2.5D movement<br></li><li>Realistic sock physics<br></li><li>Approved by the Quirk Police (\"Not too quirky, B-\")</li></ul>",
